## CUSTOM DOMAIN (Optional)
1. Buy a domain (e.g. on Namecheap or Whogohost for Nigerian domains)
2. In Vercel в†’ your project в†’ Settings в†’ Domains в†’ add your domain
3. Follow DNS instructions (usually add a CNAME record)
