## SUPPORT
If you get stuck on any step, the most common issues are:
- **Database connection fails**: Check your Supabase password has no special characters, or URL-encode them
- **CORS errors**: Make sure FRONTEND_URL in Railway exactly matches your Vercel URL (no trailing slash)
- **Paystack not loading**: Make sure VITE_PAYSTACK_PUBLIC_KEY is set in Vercel env vars and redeployed

